title: Login & Session Validation Flow
config:
  layout: elk
  look: handDrawn
  theme: dark
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Browser as 🌐 Browser
    participant Auth as 🔐 AuthContext
    participant Supabase as 📡 Supabase
    participant DB as 💾 PostgreSQL
    participant RPC as ⚙️ RPC Functions
    
    User->>Browser: 1. Enter credentials
    Browser->>Auth: 2. signInWithPassword()
    Auth->>Supabase: 3. POST /auth/v1/token
    Supabase->>Supabase: 4. Validate JWT
    Supabase-->>Auth: 5. Return JWT + user object
    
    Auth->>Supabase: 6. Fetch role from user_roles
    Supabase->>DB: 7. SELECT role FROM user_roles
    DB-->>Supabase: 8. Return role
    Supabase-->>Auth: 9. Return role
    
    Auth->>Supabase: 10. INSERT into sessions table
    Supabase->>DB: 11. INSERT session record
    DB-->>Supabase: 12. Confirmed
    Supabase-->>Auth: 13. Session created
    
    Auth->>Browser: 14. Store JWT in localStorage
    Browser->>Browser: 15. sessionStorage: store popup flag
    
    Auth-->>User: 16. Redirect to Dashboard
    
    Note over Browser,RPC: === SESSION POLLING LOOP (Every 3 seconds) ===
    
    Browser->>Auth: 17. validateSession()
    Auth->>Supabase: 18. RPC validate_session(email, token)
    Supabase->>RPC: 19. Call validation function
    RPC->>DB: 20. SELECT from sessions table
    DB-->>RPC: 21. Return session record
    
    alt Valid Session
        RPC->>RPC: 22. token matches latest session
        RPC-->>Supabase: 23. Return { valid: true }
        Supabase-->>Auth: 24. Valid response
        Auth-->>Browser: 25. Session continues
    else Session Invalid or Kicked
        RPC->>RPC: 26. token mismatch (login from another device)
        RPC-->>Supabase: 27. Return { valid: false }
        Supabase-->>Auth: 28. Invalid response
        Auth->>Browser: 29. setSessionKicked = true
        Browser->>Browser: 30. Clear localStorage (JWT, email, session)
        Auth->>Browser: 31. Show "You've been kicked out" popup
        Browser->>User: 32. Redirect to Login
    end
    
    Note over User,Browser: === LOGOUT FLOW ===
    
    User->>Browser: 33. Click Logout
    Browser->>Auth: 34. signOut()
    Auth->>Supabase: 35. DELETE from sessions
    Supabase->>DB: 36. DELETE session record
    DB-->>Supabase: 37. Confirmed
    Browser->>Browser: 38. Clear all localStorage
    Browser->>Browser: 39. Clear sessionStorage
    Browser->>User: 40. Redirect to Login page
    
